{DIALOGUE}: I mean these guys were hard-core hijackers, but there I was.
{DIALOGUE}: At that point, I wasn't scared, f knew I hadn't done anything they could do me for.
{DIALOGUE}: Besides, it was fun.
{DIALOGUE}: I got to make like I was notorious.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 12 INT. LINE-UP ROOM
