{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They are bodyguards and give it away by their every careful move.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They turn back to the elevator and motion to someone inside.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Out walks SAUL BERG, a slightly overweight man in his forties with an open collar silk shirt and a thick gold chain on his hairy chest.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He carries a LARGE ALUMINUM BRIEFCASE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He lets his guards do the worrying.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He walks straight to his car.
