{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He takes out his keys and pushes a button on his key chain.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Mercedes beeps three times and tells Saul his alarm is off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Tucci keeps an eye on McManus.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Higham watches Saul.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: McManus pretends to tinker with the car's engine.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He has put a pistol just inside the grill and keeps it within reach.
