{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It cruises over toward the Mercedes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Tucci sees the van.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He and Higham are suddenly busy trying to keep track.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They hear laughing behind them and turn around.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: YELLOW 06/11/94
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 64.
