{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The only sound is Saul grappling with Keaton for the gun.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His arm is halfway out the window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His elbow rests in the door frame.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Keaton cannot get the gun out of his hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Finally, he pushes down with all his weight.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saul's elbow breaks backwards on the door frame.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He screams in agony.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The gun falls from his hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BLUE 06/01/94
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 66.
