{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One might note it's sturdy construction and it's convenient size.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Big enough to hold a lifetime of forgotten and disregarded notes and facts.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Years of police trivia that has been hung and forgotten with the intention of finding a use for it all someday.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One might want such a bulletin board for one's self.
